Who: Rat Trap, Quickstride
Location: Area just outside Hydras' Black Fortress

(OOC: I am assuming they are still there since I didn't see a post of
them leaving. My apologies if I missed it)

BIC:

As Quickstride and Rat Trap continue their surveillance of Hydras'
base, from above their position a rather large sensor blip began to be
made out. Distant at first but quickly approaching from above.

The energy signature is strange, reading something similar to
Cyclonus' and Scourge's signature, it reads as both Decepticon and
Unicronian. As the signature approaches it can be discerned that it is
not one large one but three individuals flying in close formation.

As they continue their approach the single signature becomes three
separate signatures, two jets, a black one on the left and a red and
white one on the right, and at the center, leading them is what would
appear at this distance to be something similar to a flying weapons
platform of some sort.

Their target would appear to be Hydras' base, although at this point
they are still small but growing shapes in the skies.

(TAG)

Preston
